  "formulaSource": "Base ductwork costs from HomeAdvisor and Angi 2025-2026 national average surveys for residential HVAC ductwork installation. Material multipliers derived from ACCA Manual D duct design standards and SMACNA (Sheet Metal and Air Conditioning Contractors' National Association) pricing guides. Project type multipliers based on HomeAdvisor demolition and new-construction survey data. Insulation adders from DOE R-value recommendations and HomeAdvisor insulation upgrade pricing. Access difficulty multipliers from Bureau of Labor Statistics Occupational Employment and Wage Statistics for HVAC installers (SOC 49-9021). Regional labor multipliers derived from BLS OES regional wage data.",
